Many people have asked: What is the efficacy of the @moderna_tx #vaccine after one dose? 

The data is limited to a median of 28 days but at 80.2% overall...

It shows that there is a 50.8% efficacy up to 14 days and a 92.1% from 14 to 28 days. #covid19 #coronavirus #covid https://t.co/XhUzuRK7LH
